      "content": "hey so i was just cutting up some veggies and the knife slipped, i have a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s kind of oozing blood and won't really stop. i have some manuka honey in the cupboard, can i just put that on the cut and bandage it up so i don't have to go to the clinic? feels like it might be enough to stop the bleeding and heal it up",
